{"tid":1671201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國貨櫃車發現39具屍體　司機涉謀殺被捕","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:40:04.000Z","uid":261873,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0f841d4074c283f4d0610d2bda63722c11aae61b","tid":1671201,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=367317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D367317&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=624404a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D367317&h=d68cc92b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=367317</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】英國警方在一架貨櫃車發現39具屍體，以涉嫌謀殺罪拘捕25歲的司機。<br />\n<br />\n案發在倫敦東部埃塞克斯郡一個工業區，警方表示相信貨櫃車由保加利亞經威爾士入境英國，全部人當場證實死亡，絕大部分是成年人，一人是年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n警方正在確認死者身分，由於人數眾多，可能需要較長時間。<br />\n<br />\n涉案司機來自北愛爾蘭，警方會扣留他問話。"},{"pid":"90749522f249bb89bcb113b8d3ac02386ae9f87a","tid":1671201,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"人蛇黎啦"},{"pid":"8ecc6ca873ed5d4254b6e14078167ede1ba94bfc","tid":1671201,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 23<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:30 英國領事館國旗人鏈</strong></span><br />\n- 英國領事館外 [以旗相認]"},{"pid":"ee996b187186bb5c1a69ab4f1929e4c0b57fa02a","tid":1671201,"uid":14377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2993bbfd8b98a22bd5a1fb59a8df12d3caf40627","tid":1671201,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco