 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce146b2ed0553ea8a4a491409ba7c460367035f5","tid":1671201,"uid":261873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"40520a0aa609057f61d7bf64a922681024f7765d","tid":1671201,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2993bbfd8b98a22bd5a1fb59a8df12d3caf40627","tid":1671201,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:27:37.000Z","msg":"偷運人蛇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:29:10.000Z","msg":"睇落似..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20191023/s00005/1571821748570/英貨車藏39屍-司機涉近年最大規模謀殺被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20191023%2Fs00005%2F1571821748570%2F%E8%8B%B1%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E8%97%8F39%E5%B1%8D-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=265e6976\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20191023%2Fs00005%2F1571821748570%2F%E8%8B%B1%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E8%97%8F39%E5%B1%8D-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&h=7ec48e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20191023/s00005/1571821748570/英貨車藏39屍-司機涉近年最大規模謀殺被捕</a><br />\n<br />\n英國東南部埃塞克斯郡一貨車內發現39具屍體，25歲司機被捕，當局展開近年最大規模謀殺調查。報道稱，該貨車來自東歐保加利亞。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，死者包括38名成年人和1名青少年，當局於當地時間周三（23日）凌晨1時40分（香港時間8時40分）接報到達埃塞克斯郡格雷斯市（Grays）的Waterglade Industrial Park工業園區，發現貨車內39人，全部當場證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方以涉嫌謀殺罪拘捕一名來自北愛爾蘭的25歲男子，相信是貨車司機。警方表示，相信<span style=\"color: red;\">貨車來自保加利亞</span>，於上周六（19日）經威爾斯一個港口入境。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）"},{"pid":"73fd99f6f3bd941e6680188635aeda971a09883e","tid":1671201,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rWyof9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rWyof9.gif&h=0c250780&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3af55a1497810fa86d7244945ab62526492e7779","tid":1671201,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:38:06.000Z","msg":"焗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4913d1915469d643e5e5f018962f5c0e7ed8d010","tid":1671201,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"連登神探出嚟查案未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb2a274cf5865d00738227830abe0b52f343583","tid":1671201,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"吉良吉影?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5851c7221846fc3a6c8db03cc7b1bb38feaf5c4f","tid":1671201,"uid":297045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"印象中好多年前有單案係講福建人偷渡去英國, 但貨櫃車內無充夠流通空氣, 所以d人局死左"},{"pid":"ace315b28756f6f66194cf3d47475ab7d811875c","tid":1671201,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=312cb59e\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a5c449e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=94c966ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=fed70589\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"44c72e6d8720c97499b3b2d089a7caba20831439","tid":1671201,"uid":1043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5851c7221846fc3a6c8db03cc7b1bb38feaf5c4f","tid":1671201,"uid":297045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"印象中好多年前有單案係講福建人偷渡去英國, 但貨櫃車內無充夠流通空氣, 所以d人局死左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"巴打你講中左..."},{"pid":"72f9f4b9529c8b0d09e91ba77ec11016020815c5","tid":1671201,"uid":175511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"連登神探出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6816239d36f7df311c83392c2abb604089787b57","tid":1671201,"uid":126868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f841d4074c283f4d0610d2bda63722c11aae61b","tid":1671201,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=367317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D367317&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=624404a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D367317&h=d68cc92b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=367317</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】英國警方在一架貨櫃車發現39具屍體，以涉嫌謀殺罪拘捕25歲的司機。<br />\n<br />\n案發在倫敦東部埃塞克斯郡一個工業區，警方表示相信貨櫃車由保加利亞經威爾士入境英國，全部人當場證實死亡，絕大部分是成年人，一人是年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n警方正在確認死者身分，由於人數眾多，可能需要較長時間。<br />\n<br />\n涉案司機來自北愛爾蘭，警方會扣留他問話。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"全部中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f7bbf67916593cbedd193f160b7e48516ce167","tid":1671201,"uid":46614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"英國當局繼續調查貨櫃車內發現39具遺體的案件，英國有傳媒引述消息報道，死者全部是中國人。警方派員搜查北愛爾蘭兩處地方，相信與被捕的北愛爾蘭25歲貨櫃車司機有關連。<br />\n<br />\n警方形容事件是悲劇，首要工作是確認死者身分，預計過程漫長。<br />\n<br />\n警方說涉案車輛在保加利亞註冊，拖頭是從比利時的澤布魯日登上渡輪，在英國時間星期三凌晨零時30分，抵達英國東部埃塞克斯地區的瑟羅克市。警方在貨櫃內發現39名死者，當中包括1名未成年人。男司機涉嫌謀殺被捕。專責打擊犯罪的部門說，會派員協助警方調查案件是否涉及有組織罪案。"},{"pid":"5db6f6ecbd49713e8bb62863303c32d5bb3071ae","tid":1671201,"uid":271289,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"全部中國人<br />\n<br />\n英國貨櫃藏屍案據報39名死者是中國人<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488038-20191024.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488038-20191024.htm&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=07c7fa84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488038-20191024.htm&h=f40b20aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488038-20191024.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4593a5a033ba0edf50d2cd762550119d4213a0f9","tid":1671201,"uid":38533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"中國人"},{"pid":"b2fd23344e6b5c62da7a782096fd173057ae47be","tid":1671201,"uid":288393,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"全部支那蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f8ceed7c721a6789d3a27de15b8406db34285b","tid":1671201,"uid":31738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:56:33.000Z","msg":"有無人答到我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}